# API Configuration
# Recommended: Create a new API key at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# Then add it to AI Studio -> Settings -> Secrets as one of:
# GEMINI_API_KEY_2=your_new_api_key
# USER_GEMINI_KEY=your_new_api_key

# Alternatively, the app will check for:
# GEMINI_API, GEMINI_API_KEY, or GOOGLE_API_KEY

